Charles E. Dwyer, defendant in error, v. First Trust & Savings Bank, plaintiff in error.Gen. No. 33,992.Heard in the third division of this court for the first district at the December term, 1929.

Friend, J., not participating.

Opinion filed October 29, 1930.Amberg, Ott, Dalilin & Livingston, for plaintiff in error. Barrett, Barrett & Wermuth, for defendant in error. Mr. Presiding Justice Wilson

delivered the opinion of the court.
